-- 
Former Greek Premier Supports Debt Restructure, To Vima Reports

-- B y   M a r i a   P e t r a k i s
-- 
2011-04-17T16:09:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-17/former-greek-premier-supports-debt-restructure-to-vima-reports.html
Former socialist Prime Minister
Costas Simitis believes  Greece  should restructure its debt, To
Vima newspaper reported, citing an interview.  Opposition to restructuring from officials including
European Central Bank President Jean-Claude Trichet indicates
their concerns about the stability of the euro and repercussions
on the euro countries, the Athens-based newspaper quoted Simitis
as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Petrakis at 
